---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Tagline from '../../components/Tagline.astro';
import ServiceIcon from '../../components/ServiceIcon.astro';
---

<Layout title="Discovery & Strategy - Wellmade" description="Not sure what to build? Let's find out. By building, not by writing documents nobody reads.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-primary has-blobs py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <ServiceIcon name="discovery" class="w-14 h-14 text-accent mb-6" />
      <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-4">Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">Discovery & Strategy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80">
        Not sure what to build? Let's find out.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 mt-4">
        You have an idea. A problem. A hunch. But not a spec. That's fine. We figure it out together - by building, not by writing documents nobody reads.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why It Matters -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Why it matters.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Most projects fail before they start.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Wrong assumptions. Wrong priorities. A beautifully detailed spec for something nobody actually wants.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        Discovery isn't a phase you skip to save money. It's how you avoid wasting money on the wrong thing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What It Looks Like -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-12">What it looks like.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Understanding the real problem.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Not what stakeholders think users want. What users actually need. We dig, we question, we challenge assumptions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Talking to real people.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">We want access to actual users. Not proxies. Not personas. Real humans with real problems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Prototyping fast.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Ideas are cheap. Working prototypes reveal what slides can't. We build rough, we learn fast, we refine.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Testing assumptions.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Before you invest in building the full thing, we test the risky parts. Technical feasibility. User interest. Business model.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card md:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Aligning on what to build.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Not a 100-page document. A shared understanding. Clear priorities. A path forward.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Get -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">What you get.</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-body">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Clarity on the problem worth solving</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Validated (or invalidated) assumptions</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Working prototypes - not wireframes, real things you can click</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>A roadmap you actually believe in</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Confidence that you're building the right thing</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Who it's for.</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/80">
            <li>Founders with an idea but not a plan</li>
            <li>Companies exploring new products or markets</li>
            <li>Teams stuck in analysis paralysis</li>
            <li>Anyone who's been burned by building the wrong thing before</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Who it's not for.</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/80">
            <li>"We already know what we want, just build it" projects</li>
            <li>Clients who can't give us access to real users or real context</li>
            <li>Discovery as a checkbox before the "real work" starts</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-white/90 mt-6 font-medium">Discovery is the real work. If you're not ready to learn and adapt, we're not the right fit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Happens After -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">What happens after.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Discovery often flows into Product Development. But not always.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Sometimes we discover you shouldn't build anything. Sometimes the answer is simpler than expected. Sometimes it's more complex.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        We'll tell you what we find. Honestly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work Together -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">How we work together.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We work in days. Flexible, transparent, no surprises.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Discovery engagements are typically short and focused - enough to answer the critical questions, not enough to become a consulting marathon.
      </p>
      <a href="/working-with-us" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-semibold hover:text-primary/70 transition-colors group">
        See how we work
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-6">Let's figure it out.</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Tagline />
</Layout>
